videos.headline: Michigan St defense forces big fumble
videos.description: Michigan State's defense comes up big as it forces Nebraska's Kade Warner to fumble.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play ( Michigan St defense forces big fumble) 2018/11/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nebraska's defense gets huge sack-fumble
videos.description: Trailing late in the 4th quarter, Nebraska's defense gets a big stop, as Antonio Reed gets a sack-fumble on Spartans' Rocky Lombardi, giving the Huskers' offense great field position.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nebraska's defense gets huge sack-fumble ) 2018/11/17 ESHEET
